                     <interp inst="t17801018-29-off149" type="offenceSubcategory" value="robbery"></interp>
               that they, in a certain dwelling-house belonging to a certain person unknown, in and upon 
                     
                        <persName id="t17801018-29-victim317" type="victimName">
                           William 
