                   feloniously did make an assault, putting him in corporeal fear and danger of his life, and stealing from his person a silver watch, value 40 s. a steel chain, value 10 d. a stone swivel seal , value 4 s. and a brass watch-key, value 1 d. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17801018-29-person318">
